WEBVTT

00:11:58.810 --> 00:12:00.861
Naručit ću vas za EKG i CT

00:12:00.861 --> 00:12:04.203
što prije."

00:12:04.203 --> 00:12:05.831
A mi si mislimo,

00:12:05.831 --> 00:12:08.771
ne, ne, ne. Nije to 
srčani udar. Može on disati,

00:12:08.771 --> 00:12:13.768
ali samo na usta. Ne, ne, ne, ne.

00:12:13.768 --> 00:12:16.031
Tako smo se natezali s ovim doktorom

00:12:16.031 --> 00:12:18.509
zato što smo mislili da 
ovo nije bila dobra dijagnoza,

00:12:18.509 --> 00:12:22.461
